18 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
19 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
20 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 34.401 of Title 62, unless there
21 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
22 In addition to other duties imposed upon the Office of
23 Management and Enterprise Services (OMES) by law, the Director of
24 the Office of Management and Enterprise Services shall ensure that
